import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.plot(data['date'], data['price'], label='Price', color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.title('What is the trend of price over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    average_price = data['price'].mean()
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.bar('Average Price', average_price, color='blue')
    ax.axhline(average_price, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Price: {average_price:.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    
    plt.title('What is the average price?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.hist(data['price'], bins=30, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='Price')
    plt.axvline(data['price'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['price'].median():.2f}")
    
    plt.xlabel('Price')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of price?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.boxplot(data['price'])
    ax.set_title('What is the highest and lowest price?')
    ax.set_ylabel('Price')
    ax.set_xticklabels(['Price'])
    
    min_price = data['price'].min()
    max_price = data['price'].max()
    
    ax.axhline(min_price, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Min Price: {min_price:.2f}')
    ax.axhline(max_price, color='green', linestyle='--', label=f'Max Price: {max_price:.2f}')
    
    ax.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
